{"tid":2061168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［仲唔認係共狗？］垃圾徵費一事熱狗泰同建制一齊投反對","createTime":"2020-06-12T07:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T09:41:49.000Z","uid":131282,"like":8,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0694193b103d9d1e47f1cb1c0f87e591a4e4cc25","tid":2061168,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"蟲太：直截了當，反對繼續審議「垃圾徵費」。<br />\n<br />\n註：據悉大部分建制派亦會同意終止 bills com，好快連登又會有 posts 抹黑我投共奶共咯～<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『垃圾徵費是苛捐雜稅，明明特區政府有龐大財政盈餘，這是蓄意擾民。』2018-12-05<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2JTXkU-XWik&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2JTXkU-XWik%26list%3DPLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjCWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=d89bd745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2JTXkU-XWik&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『許多大廈既有商業亦有住宅，有時有服務式住宅，這是否垃圾徵費的灰色地帶？是否為此要裝上閉路電視？除了實行時極為擾民，政府的公權力會否因而過度膨漲，也是值得關注的問題。』Jan 8, 2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h5BHQJTSdcY&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh5BHQJTSdcY%26list%3DPLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv%26index%3D2&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjCWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=7efb5e20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h5BHQJTSdcY&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=2</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『現在的回收商經營十分困難，很多時要將廢料棄置堆填區，垃圾徵費會否令他們運作更加困難？』2019-02-18<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Y16xwg8P2o&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4Y16xwg8P2o%26list%3DPLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv%26index%3D3&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjCWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=1637ad5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Y16xwg8P2o&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=3</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『實施垃圾徵費後，政府在公共場所棄置垃圾可以豁免，但到康文署場地運動後丟膠樽鋁罐的人隨時會被罰款。環境局為何持雙重標準？』2019-3-26<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2LHrKgwq9Tc&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2LHrKgwq9Tc%26list%3DPLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv%26index%3D4&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjCWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=7356d86d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2LHrKgwq9Tc&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=4</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『推行垃圾徵費，但房屋署會放寬招聘兼職清潔工的限制，兼職又不會獲得全職所享有的垃圾徵費豁免及保障，隨時會被罰款。這種執行細節的缺漏，是思慮不周，還是為求推行環保而不惜剝削勞工？』Mar 26, 2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IB24z0LM_9w&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIB24z0LM_9w%26list%3DPLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv%26index%3D5&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjCWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=687895e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IB24z0LM_9w&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=5</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『鄉郊地方處理垃圾不少都只是依賴鄰里，政府想到鄉郊地方處罰胡亂棄置家居垃圾的市民，根本連警察都會感到困難。』2019-3-26<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kmJfpRQ4J2I&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkmJfpRQ4J2I%26list%3DPLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv%26index%3D6&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjCWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=9ce9fbef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kmJfpRQ4J2I&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=6</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『垃圾徵費會豁免政府工人但不會豁免外判清潔工人，同樣是提供公共服務但竟然會有差別待遇。另一方面不少團體會自發清理垃圾，例如到海灘清理膠粒，他們會否誤墮法網？』<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hVXO9X6jucM&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhVXO9X6jucM%26list%3DPLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv%26index%3D7&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjCWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=388b9ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hVXO9X6jucM&amp;list=PLVhMqRPQAM5w63z4x2jB3lzjk5o2qj6Iv&amp;index=7</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『環境局推行垃圾徵費時，會假設市民會因處理垃圾成本上升而培養出垃圾回收的習慣。可是九成香港的回收商去年因大陸的「限廢令」已損失兩三成生意額，預期未來一兩年會有三成回收商要結業，城市垃圾並無多少出路。環境局對垃圾回收生態欠缺認識卻堅決推行垃圾徵費，等如妨礙城市基建(infrastructure)的運作。』May 7,<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『實施垃圾徵費後，政府以離島人口不多為由，將多個離島的廢物轉運設施處置垃圾收費劃一，這是十分粗疏和官僚的做法。離島的人口相差甚遠，長洲最少有二萬人，南丫島大約六千；日後再於喜靈洲建人工島遷入大量住戶，環境局是否又會繼續這種不公的做法？』May 20, 2019<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『創科局食衛局都熱衷在各區放置攝錄鏡頭，聲稱是拍到有人亂拋垃圾的影片，警務處可否隨意取用？』2019-12-18<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『垃圾徵費立法的原意是減少丟棄垃圾，目標是2021年實施，而現在開始招標的公屋模擬垃圾徵費計劃是向住戶提供專用膠袋直至2023年，以評估垃圾量的影響，但沒有財政誘因，想有資料都難。模擬計劃的兩年空<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『垃圾徵費要求「指定膠袋不能有固體廢物掉出」，但平日出入或會不慎被外物刮穿，或是膠袋太小無法妥善裝載大件垃圾，結果工友和住客每天都有機會誤墮法網。』May 20, 2020<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：『垃圾徵費實行後，局方會容許部份謀利業務免費供應指定垃圾袋，究竟會如何界定謀利或非謀利業務？整條垃圾徵費法案，似乎連釋義都是不清不楚的。』Jun 3, 2020<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8ynhMF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8ynhMF.jpg&h=3bb8450e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你連垃圾徵費都反對 仲點光復香港？"},{"pid":"65b8da0e66e80d7559db3f07fe076f159e225154","tid":2061168,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"Source: Facebook"},{"pid":"12a4556ec3d33b568cc903a9588a852c6a66b74c","tid":2061168,"uid":31237,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:56:37.000Z","msg":"反對垃圾徵費有咩問題？<br />\n要收收生產商錢 做咩要收市民錢？<br />\n而且而家要回收咁麻煩<br />\n之前咩四電一腦又係搶錢"},{"pid":"cdd3ad78b61ac7bedd171b8eea2788856bac27e6","tid":2061168,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"12a4556ec3d33b568cc903a9588a852c6a66b74c","tid":2061168,"uid":31237,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyT